@UTF8
changed from 07 to 08 

1) Compound verbs regrouped
syntactic compound verbs as v+v , lexial compounds as v (stem v_v)
following 影山太郎 (2013） NINJAL複合動詞レキシコン <vvlexicon.ninjal.ac.jp>
listed in verb.cut

syntactic: tabehajimeru v:v|+v:v|tabe+v:v|hajime-PRES=start_to_eat
lexical: tabekobos v:c|tabe_kobos-PRES=spill_food

n|+v:c|fum+v:c|kir-GER=railroad_crossing -> n|fumikiri=railroad_crossing

2) new: (v:cop) no v:cop|da&ADN:no=be
	inu no omawarisan v:cop|no&ADN=be
	 (compare: inu no shippo ptl:attr|no=GEN)
	kugatsu kara (yori) no kyuuka   -> kugatsu kara da
    kugatsu made no kyuuka
    iku made no aida
    ni oite no 
    ni kanshite no
    x mite no kansoo

3) Modal expressions revised
a) new: (v:sub) naranai v:c:sub|nar-NEG-PRES=PRH  (nakute wa naranai , nakereba naranai)
b) new: (v:sub) ikemasen v:c:sub|ik-POT-POL-NEG:n&PRES=PRH etc (nakute wa ikemasen; wake ni wa ikanai )
c) new: (v:sub) ni kimatteru v:cop|ni&ADV=be v:c:sub|kimar-ASP-PRES=be_decided) only CONN and ASP-PRES
d) new: (smod) nichigainai smod|ni_chigai_nai=no_doubt_that
     nichigainakatta smod|ni_chigai_nakatta=no_doubt_that
     nichigaiarimasen smod|ni_chigai_arimasen=no_doubt_that
e) change: (smod) rashii
	OLD smod|rashii=hearsay  -> NEW smod|rashi-PRES
	iku rashii       smod|rashi-PRES
	iku rashikute    smod|rashi-CONN    
	iku rashiku      smod|rashi-ADV
   cut:  rashii adj|rashi-PRES=seeming  
	(compare: harurashii  haru-rashi-PRES, -PAST NEG-PRES etc)
	
f) new: (fml) no (da)  n:fml|no=RLV
	OLD ptl:snr|no=SNR v:cop|da&PRES=be
	NEW n:fml|no=RLV v:cop|da&PRES=be
	(compare: iku no ga ii  ptl:snr|no=SNR )

h) new: (fml) koto n:fml|koto=IMP
	te arau koto! -> n:fml|koto=IMP
	(compare: iku koto ga ooi  n:fml|koto=fact )

i) new: (infl) -zaru NEG:zaru

j) new: (sub) eru  v:v:sub|e-PRES=get
	tabezaru o enai  
	v:v|tabe-NEG:zaru=eat ptl:case|o=ACC v:v:sub|e-NEG-PRES=get

k) new: (infl) -e(ru)  POT:e
%%%%%%cr.cut laeuft noch nicht v-pot-vv2  (und infl fuer i-infl muss auch rein)
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
zaru o enai   =>>    NEG:zaru   v:v:sub|e-NEG   
narieru  ==> POT:e
nariuru  ==> POT:u

l) change: (smod) tsutsu	
   OLD smod|tsutsu=in_course_of
   	   smod|tsutsu_aru=in_course_of
   NEW  -CONN:tsutsu  
   ikitsutsu aru v:c|ik-CONN:tsutsu=go v:ir:sub|ar-PRES=be

m) change: (smod) bakari
   OLD smod|bakari=nothing_but		
   NEW ptl:foc|bakari=nothing_but
   (compare: n:fml|bakari=nothing_but)

%%%%%%%%%%%bishier
